rgin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322120426pl5LDATIMo3nSW7P.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322120428gix345LwYndABjWy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322120428br359iRYvpN8lj4W.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322120429URiqTeFzjhwbGMQl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322120430OrMD0Fp9VUQGmSWl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322120433qX3lxpFBkGIsKnVy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Everlane-to-launch-an-underwear-line-designed-with-women-s-comfort-in-mind,960721.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Everlane 推出了首个男女装内衣系列</a>，包括文胸、内衣裤，将于 3 月 26 日正式上架。该系列保持了 Everlane 一贯的简洁风，它请来女演员 Jemima Kirke 做模特，花了两年时间完善了近 40 个不同的样品。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322120340NV3zYK1tG6hUTWEr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.563077\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>这个周末，潮店<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2018/3/sean-wotherspoon-nike-air-max-1-97-van-solebox\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Solebox</a> 和 Nike Air Max 1/97 的合作款即将发售，Solebox 特意定制了一台与鞋面配色相同的厢式货车，在阿姆斯特丹的街头卖鞋，这方式也是蛮酷的。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322120318LMRoDuHA46rVS2aw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180322120314rfEYsWCjSKceou4w.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803221203141JtBbA4z6FxRodyw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201803221203142x7qbU5BOIlaRcLz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：The Weeknd</p>"}